{"tid":374313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 去旅行落機同人掉轉左行李箱","createTime":"2017-08-25T15:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T01:46:56.000Z","uid":39528,"like":31,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4afccdd5bf1bf271a58f476e1c5f746f8f79cce9","tid":374313,"uid":39528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"事源係因為兩個行李個箱係一樣樣<br />\n咁我就好遲先去拎行李 咁我見個gip一樣樣<br />\n咁我就冇睇寄艙個name tag就拎走左<br />\n事後去到飯店想開gip先知拎錯左<br />\n跟著打去台中機場問 佢地話只可以等另一個人<br />\n都打去通知 先可以做到野<br />\n但其實係另外果個拎錯左先<br />\n而家等左成日都冇消息<br />\n各位巴絲有咩方法可以搵得番自己個gip<br />\n<br />\n而家冇衫褲換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"968d7961af2051ed653b2133bfdc50dbeeaf9891","tid":374313,"uid":39528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e22c09ff9f29963df4b71dc5b47d75a40a9ba79","tid":374313,"uid":118842,"like":4,"dislike":51,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"點解可以開到個gip"},{"pid":"97964bfb7a98fced380d88a6772fb10a591fad56","tid":374313,"uid":86753,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我成日去旅行都驚依樣野所以痴好多野"},{"pid":"f547407a42fc3c21a5ca8d43a2cd58eb552331a3","tid":374313,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"唯有等，聽日出機場拎返<br />\n<br />\nbtw 你都拎錯啦"},{"pid":"072e2cf1dc3808defa23fbcade24bd25619203b6","tid":374313,"uid":39528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以開到個gip</blockquote><br />\n就係開唔到個gip再望下個name tag先知唔係我嘅<img src=\"/asset